<br>
She headed inside and sat on the bed, looking around. She loved decorating her huts in different villages, it was always so much fun, and each hut had something special about it, something unique that the others didn't.<br>
<br>
She set out several scrolls on the table in the center, along with bottles of ink and quills. <br>
<br>
She leaned her staff up against the wall and kicked off her shoes at the foot of the bed.<br>
<br>
&quot;It's beginning to look like home already.&quot;<br>
